    "Background": {
      "text": "Potentially fatal syndrome\nAssociated with\naspirin\nuse during\nviral illness\n, especially\ninfluenza\n,\nvaricella\nMultiorgan system disease, particularly effects brain and liver\nClassic early symptoms:\nrash\n,\nvomiting\n,\nliver damage\n(without\njaundice\ntypically)\n[1]",
