    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Stage I\nRash\non palms of hands and feet\nPersistent, heavy\nvomiting\nAltered mental status\n,\nconfusion\n, generalized\nlethargy\nHigh\nfever\nStage II\nStupor\nHyperventilation\nFatty liver (found by biopsy)\nStage III\nPossible\ncoma\nPossible cerebral edema\nRarely,\nrespiratory arrest\nStage IV\nDeepening\ncoma\nDilated pupils with minimal response to light\nMinimal hepatic dysfunction\nStage V\nDeep\ncoma\nSeizures\nMultisystem organ failure[7]\nFlaccidity\nHyperammonemia (above 300mg/dL of blood)\nDeath",
